      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented regression test suite covering hemolysis-relevant flow regimes; formal change-control process in place.",
      "rationale": "Solver is version-controlled and regression tests exist for canonical pipe-flow and rotating-disk cases. However, no hemolysis-specific regression suite is maintained and change-control documentation is incomplete for the turbulence model update applied in this study. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
    },
