      "rationale": "E_rms computed at all 5 points; experimental uncertainty from repeat trials included. Systematic bias of +12% at high-flow operating points not fully explained. Validation uncertainty U_val exceeds required threshold at 2 of 5 points. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
