      "rationale": "Validation QoI is NIH consistent with submission QoI. However, the hemolysis accumulation model integrates shear stress along Lagrangian particle paths, and path-integrated stress is not independently validated — only the integrated NIH output is compared. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
